ety i komentarze. To \u015bwietny spos\u00f3b, aby dowiedzie\u0107 si\u0119, co mo\u017cna poprawi\u0107 w Twoich listingach.<\/li>\n<li><b>Testowanie obraz\u00f3w<\/b> \u2013 Rozwa\u017c u\u017cycie narz\u0119dzi do test\u00f3w A\/B, aby sprawdzi\u0107, kt\u00f3re zdj\u0119cia produkt\u00f3w dzia\u0142aj\u0105 najlepiej. To mo\u017ce pom\u00f3c w zwi\u0119kszeniu konwersji.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, optymalizacja listing\u00f3w na Amazonie to proces, kt\u00f3ry wymaga uwagi i zaanga\u017cowania. Wykorzystaj powy\u017csze wskaz\u00f3wki, aby zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 atrakcyjno\u015b\u0107 swoich ofert i lepiej odpowiada\u0107 na potrzeby klient\u00f3w.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak zoptymalizowa\u0107 swoje produkty na Amazonie?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si\u0119, jak poprawi\u0107 swoje o<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":7110,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7109","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-ecommerce"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7109"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7109"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7109\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7110"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=710